on-announced-260894.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。史克威尔艾尼克斯在2013年9月注册“Bravely Second”商标<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/09/18/hey-these-trademarks-sound-like-future-bravely-default-games/ |title=Hey, These Trademarks Sound Like Future Bravely Default Games |author=Ishaan |publisher=Siliconera |date=2013-09-18 |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2013-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208142958/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/09/18/hey-these-trademarks-sound-like-future-bravely-default-games/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并在2013年12月期的《[[Jump|Jump]]》杂志上正式宣布游戏名称<ref name="Eurogamer1">{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Tom |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-12-04-bravely-default-sequel-announced-for-3ds-in-japan |title=Bravely Default sequel announced for 3DS in Japan • News • 3DS • |publisher=Eurogamer |date= |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2015-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001014633/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-12-04-bravely-default-sequel-announced-for-3ds-in-japan |dead-url=no }}</ref>——根据“勇气默示录 For the Sequel”游戏机制命名的“勇气默示录2”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2013/12/04/bravely-second-announced-as-sequel-to-bravely-default/ |title=Bravely Second announced as sequel to Bravely Default |last=Nunneley |first=Stephany |publisher=VG247 |date=2013-12-04 |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207060053/http://www.vg247.com/2013/12/04/bravely-second-announced-as-sequel-to-bravely-default/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随之公布的只有游戏平台为[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/12/bravely_default_sequel_confirmed_for_3ds_in_japan |title=Bravely Default Sequel Confirmed for 3DS in Japan |last=Whitehead |first=Thomas |publisher=Nintendolife |date=2012-12-04 |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2013-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206014019/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/12/bravely_default_sequel_confirmed_for_3ds_in_japan |dead-url=no }}</ref>。尚未有非日本（或日语）版本发行的公告<ref name="kotaku1" />。游戏在2013年12月大约完工30%<ref name="sildec10" />。

2013年12月有消息透漏吉田已经离开史克威尔<ref name="polygon2">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/12/5/5177724/bravely-default-character-designer-leaves-square-enix |title=Bravely Default character designer leaves Square Enix |author=Gera, Emily |publisher=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |date=2013-12-05 |accessdate=2013-12-05 |archive-date=2013-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208142733/http://www.polygon.com/2013/12/5/5177724/bravely-default-character-designer-leaves-square-enix |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他称仍计划创作勇气默示录游戏<ref name="Eurogamer1" />。虽然他称《勇气默示录2》仍然延续前作的[[日本动画|动画]]画风<ref name="Eurogamer1" />，但角色略微靠近现实[[头身|比例]]，低身长设计略有弱化<ref name="sildec10">{{cite web |author=Ishaan |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/10/bravely-second-will-larger-fields-things/ |title=Bravely Second Will Have Larger Fields, More Things To Do |publisher=Siliconera |date=2013-12-10 |accessdate=2013-12-14 |archive-date=2013-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214042859/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/10/bravely-second-will-larger-fields-things/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最初的討論之下诞生了马格诺利娅身着宇航服或兔耳的理念，但最終因為“成人外观”而废弃，开发人员认为某些重要元素在第一作中有失<ref>{{cite web |author=Sato |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/12/bravely-second-producer-aims-create-new-pillar-support-square-enix/ |title=Bravely Second Producer Aims To Create A New Pillar Of Support For Square Enix |publisher=Siliconera |date= |accessdate=2013-12-14 |archive-date=2013-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216045815/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/12/bravely-second-producer-aims-create-new-pillar-support-square-enix/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。浅野还确认游戏会延续前作的故事导向，而非改为探险导向<ref name="BraveSecInterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/02/21/bravely-second-will-focus-story-rather-exploration/|title=Bravely Second Will Focus On Story Rather Than Exploration|author=Ishaan|publisher=Siliconera|date=2014-02-21|accessdate=2014-02-22|archive-date=2014-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301183706/http://www.siliconera.com/2014/02/21/bravely-second-will-focus-story-rather-exploration/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年4月，制作人浅野在《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》的传言栏中宣称游戏剧本已经完成<ref>{{cite web |author=Mauro Piccillo |url=http://www.eirgames.com/13580/bravely-second-scenario-completato/ |title=Bravely Second Scenario Compleato! |publisher=EIR Games |date= |accessdate=2014-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413125906/http://www.eirgames.com/13580/bravely-second-scenario-completato/ |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《Fami通》杂志在2014年7月下旬报道[[Revo|Revo]]因时间表冲突，将不再为游戏谱写原声，[[Supercell|Supercell]]乐团的Ryo将接替此职务<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sato|title=Supercell’s ryo In Charge Of Music For Bravely Second|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2014/07/29/supercells-ryo-charge-music-bravely-second/|website=Siliconera|accessdate=2014-07-29|archive-date=2014-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801090524/http://www.siliconera.com/2014/07/29/supercells-ryo-charge-music-bravely-second/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==

中国大陆电子游戏杂志《[[游戏机实用技术|游戏机实用技术]]》打出24/30的高分，称赞游戏比前作更加庞大的职业系统<ref>{{cite journal|title=黄金眼|journal=游戏机实用技术|year=2015|issue=370|page=14}}</ref>。

== 后续 ==
2019年12月，史克威尔艾尼克斯在[[游戏大奖|游戏大奖2019]]上公布了《[[勇气默示录II|勇气默示录II]]》，游戏将计划于2020年在[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]上发售。

